OL,3,CGo North East workers consulted on
OL,4,Cpotential strike action in management
OL,5,Crow
OL,7,FUnite regional officer Dave Telford
OL,8,Fadded: "Once again, communities are
OL,9,Fbeing betrayed by Go North East. Our
OL,10,Fmembers live and work in this area and
OL,11,Fthe working conditions they now face
OL,12,Fare so unreasonable they are
OL,13,Fconsidering strike action. Passengers
OL,14,Fare being put in danger by this
OL,15,Fapproach to safety.
OL,17,F"Deciding to de-recognise our reps is
OL,18,Fan act of absurd cowardice. Imagine if
OL,19,Funions refused to deal with managers
OL,20,Fwho they didn't like.
