OL,3,CGo North East workers consulted on
OL,4,Cpotential strike action in management
OL,5,Crow
OL,7,FIn response, Go North East
OL,8,Fspokesperson said: "Go North East is
OL,9,Fcommitted to ensuring the highest
OL,10,Fsafety standards at all times.
OL,11,FRecently, we introduced safety
OL,12,Fbriefings for drivers to reinforce
OL,13,Fbest practices, for example to ensure
OL,14,Fthat double deck buses are not driven
OL,15,Fon routes with low bridges in case it
OL,16,Fleads to bridge strikes. Safety
OL,17,Fstandards of this nature are essential
OL,18,Ffor protecting our passengers.
OL,26,@pD@TOU
