OL,3,CGo North East workers consulted on
OL,4,Cpotential strike action in management
OL,5,Crow
OL,7,F"Over 99% of drivers supported this
OL,8,Fbut a very small number of drivers
OL,9,F(seven out of 1300) initially declined
OL,10,Fto sign up to the safety standards or
OL,11,Fprovide assurances that they would
OL,12,Fadhere to these safe ways of working.
OL,13,FIn accordance with our established
OL,14,Fprocedures, these drivers were
OL,15,Ftemporarily suspended. However, the
OL,16,Fissue was resolved, and the
OL,17,Fsuspensions lifted."
